title: Random Story Idea
content: Inspired by Lagos nightlife: a young DJ falls for a dancer who only performs to afrobeat tracks like Nobody Fine Pass you. she's the daugther of a strict politician who disapproves. Plot twist: she's secretly a math teacher by day, using her earnings to fund a community sschool. Write a short story about their clash of worlds - music, love, and ambition.
